These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-1::.
There 2 different types of food: eggplant, broccoli
1. the person eating eggplant is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |    2    |
| Food   | eggplant | broccoli |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-2::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: disaster, epic
1. the person watching epic movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | epic |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: trance, ambient
1. the fan of trance is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |   2   |
| Music-Genre   | ambient | trance |

